race.comment: LOVE MY KUNA (5) copped a check in the run last time and never threatened when sixth (18.08) in a LS6 at this track. Well worth another try. FIRE FLY CAROLE (1) collided with another runner and finished a well held 15 lengths eighth (18.56) last time in a LS6 at this track over 297m. May be worth another try. PUMBAA SMITH (4) has shown good improvement at his last two starts, hitting the frame latest when 2nd at this track over 297m. Hard to beat again. YOU GOT ME (7) can measure up with the right run.
